Textual Confirmation protects only the registration page. To protect everything, use the new tool <a href="http://bbantispam.com/atc/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Advanced Textual Confirmation</a>. Here is the description how to <a href="http://bbantispam.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=284" target="_blank" class="postlink">stop phpBB spam</a> using ATC.
<br />

